				<li id="16454988" class="cmnt-root" data="21" data-d="1646450813000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t579509/Night-Shard" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">04 Mar 2022 22:26</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16454988" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">In general case, this spell does not compete well will Pebble. (same cost but with shorter range + lower dmg + no tracking). However, from my personal testing its casting time + projectile speed is faster than the Pebble. This is especially handy for agile enemy. <br/><br/>A great example can be Godskin Apostle in Divine Tower of Caelid, the speed difference will render one spell as normal dmg and the other is almost useless in a solo situation. This spell can single handle this boss in a cheating way. <br/><br/>Because of this shorter range + faster projectile + still pretty fp efficient, it actually serves as a middle ground between Pebble (long dist one point dmg) and Carian Slicer and finally becomes my tech choice against lots of annoying invaders or agile boss for my sorcery buid.<br/><br/>P.S. Does not work well with dog-type enemies where they perform left/right dodge.<br/></p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16454988" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16454988" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">3</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>25</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>4</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16454988"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16454988" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16454988"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
